::Shredder/Grimmler::

Shredder frowns. "Now wait a min..." his voice trails off as he looks at the 
eight bots, realizing that a battle with then wouldn't be too great.

"Why of course," he says, gesturing toward the base, "RIght this way."

He had betrayed many factions in his life, if this didn't work out, another 
betrayal wouldn't be too bad. He was a better traitor than leader anyways.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Grimmler frowns, nodding. "I see... What kind of effect would this key have 
on us?"
